  characterDataArray:
  - Name: REIMU HAKUREI
    colorName: {r: 1, g: 0.06666667, b: 0.06666667, a: 1}
    Sprite: {fileID: 7057801135558962131, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    Sprite_shadow: {fileID: 5125949765403844629, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    subdesc: MYSTERIOUS FLYING SHRINE MAIDEN
    colorSubdes: {r: 1, g: 0.06666667, b: 0.06666667, a: 1}
    desc: The soldiers from the Pure Land finally made an entrance. Their flawlessness
      rejected the life and death of living creatures.
  - Name: SANAE KOCHIYA
    colorName: {r: 0.26666668, g: 0.86666673, b: 0, a: 1}
    Sprite: {fileID: 831530178016107049, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    Sprite_shadow: {fileID: 734498035006322362, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    subdesc: MIRACULOUS LIVING GOD RESIDING ON THE MOUNTAIN
    colorSubdes: {r: 0.13333334, g: 0.73333335, b: 0, a: 1}
    desc: A metallic spider appeared over the Youkai Mountain. To her, it looked
      like the Mars rover, Curiosity.
  - Name: MARISA KIRISAME
    colorName: {r: 1, g: 0.8000001, b: 0, a: 1}
    Sprite: {fileID: -3993211317029401747, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    Sprite_shadow: {fileID: 887505566864250341, guid: 65e90fd085f92db459b86e370aeff497, type: 3}
    subdesc: AN ORDINARY MAGICIAN
    colorSubdes: {r: 0.8000001, g: 0.4666667, b: 0, a: 1}
    desc: The Lunar Capital's Power Stone appeared before anyone knew it. It held
      a power that could throw Gensokyo's society into chaos.
